<p>Applicants for this role must a qualified accountant with relevant experience partnering the business in a decision support or partnering position. Applicants will be able to show how they have added value to the business and where they have assisted in the development of the financial plan for stakeholders. A commercial eye is key as well as the ability to explain financials to the wider business community. Strong data manipulation skills are expected using excel.</p>
<p> </p>
<p>In return the successful applicants will get the chance to work for businesses that are able to take a solid financial controls and accounting background and give a real commercial focus and edge to their CV.</p>
